dct_title_s: Central Park. / produced by Central Park Visitor Services ; design by Heidi Humphrey/H+. (Text)
dct_description_sm: Panel title: Central Park map and guide. "Published in cooperation with City of New York Department of Parks & Recreation." Includes indexes to fountains and sculpture, named gates, arches and bridges, points of interest, public facilities, and service facilities. Text, indexes, directories, and illustrations on verso.
dct_publisher_sm: Central Park, N.Y. : New York City Dept. of Parks & Recreation, 1988.
